{
  "stem": "6878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he pushed me through the gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I walked across the two bridges, which I had to cross to go to the farm, having my little boy on my shoulders-- he was blonde-- and singing Lithuanian songs past the police, the police and military Germans, and so on.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they did, they just smiled at me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just laughed at me that I'm singing to my little boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, obviously, she went through a very, very hard time, and the same as us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were freed by the Russians, we walked around in many, many places to look.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe there's a mistake or so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we found out that he was killed by the Lithuanian where he was kept, but this is still to come.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't mention-- I didn't mention when I started off in Russia, walked into Lithuania-- I didn't mention that after a couple of months, the Russians arrested the rich people from Lithuania, and they deported them to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They kept them on the railway station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They kept them three days without water and food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were in that area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could-- we know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, after the war, some of them survived but most of them not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will carry on with this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I took out my little boy that night, the ghetto was surrounded by hundreds of police and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that night they took out about 10,000 people from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My wife managed to survive because we had a little pantry in the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a little pantry there with firewood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she climbed in between the firewood, and she covered herself with firewood, with logs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they came in to search, they didn't find anybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
